snippet.description:
Why Top Movie Studios WON'T SIGN Amber Heard | Celebrity Craze

We are unsure of Amber Heard’s professional acting career in Hollywood at the moment. This is because she is currently fighting major court cases against her ex-husband, Johnny Depp. The case is one that is revealing bad things about her and her reputation. 

From this several fans have expressed their own personal desires to have her removed from role, Mira, in Aquaman 2. Because of all of this one can clearly see that she has gotten herself in a lot of trouble and is now currently looking to make a jump into another major movie franchise, if that is even possible.
